{"TopicId":215630,"ForumId":197,"TopicTitle":"Medium Wings Pitch is Inverted","CreatedByName":"rogue_luke","CreatedById":228098,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-20T20:27:34Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"rogue_luke","CreatedById":228098,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-20T20:27:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Pitch on medium wings is incorrect vs all other control surfaces/stabilizers/wings so that when mounted behind the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECOM\u003C/abbr\u003E the control surface will angle down to the ground instead of up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP 1 if this issue cropped up you could invert the control surfaces and it would solve the issue, however in KSP 2 inverting controls also inverting the roll controls which makes it almost impossible to fly anything intuitively.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00226Yv9cTG.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/6Yv9cTG.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022zZOdFpF.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002252.07\u0022 height=\u0022441\u0022 width=\u0022847\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/zZOdFpF.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022DkxTtP8.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/DkxTtP8.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}